description: This Chainlink VRF common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 6, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 12, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, 8 for East, Box for South, and 8 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [12 Votes, Common]
